com.simulus

Class EditorApp

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • com.simulus.EditorApp

  • public class EditorApp
extends javafx.application.Application
    EditorApp represents the map editor of the Simulus suite. It should not be used as a run-target but only be started through the Startup application.
